reviewText:
A Co-Worker of mine had been wanting to get Soloman & Sheeba.  Well Considaring the Blu-Ray is $50 to $60, he decided have me purchase this double feature with Soloman & Sheeba in it until the Blu-Ray becomes more affordable.
  Needless to say...he loves it
A classic worth adding to ones library. Memorable.
Forgot how Bad acting was when this film was made..
